{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "e0713991-4955-4d0e-960b-d7ebf5ed70af",
    "name": "TerkOffice 05: Spying on Gerhard",
    "sceneId": "60cb5886-83dd-4e8f-9953-a9eafd43c179",
    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "c4da9148-46f2-40a7-b626-40725bcebfd2",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "d159d82d-ae02-4c3f-84a2-bb13cc072602",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "I had correspondence with your Patron recently. He's very disappointed in you, as well he should be.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "161d5b8e-5409-44c5-b054-4580f0b0c347",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "So tell me, what have you learned so far... Do you have anything that will incriminate Master von Urwald?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "36ccb677-705b-4d9c-b033-e9332f9d4379",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "9258062a-b06e-46b4-aa29-bdcfe848c702",
                            "text": "Tell the Truth",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "d71fa0dc-7f07-49d8-94db-1f8e7de4e8b7",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "39",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "622c0073-8ebf-4017-8d99-953cd8c945b1",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "I have to get into Gerhard's office to find incriminating evidence, but the door is trapped. I'm building up my skills with lock picks enough so that I can safely open the door.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "758466f0-c7e6-4296-bb0d-624467e825c9",
                                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Then you should be off practicing your skills rather than wasting my time!",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "750536e0-e39a-4be5-b1c4-f4fe57c73cca",
                            "text": "Bluff",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "3eeab516-8d2f-4385-9d1c-aece5e7e9c3e",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "39",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6b610bb2-2fca-4d51-854c-90aa9ef85446",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "I listened in on a conversation between Gerhard talking to Sosi about the black market Gerhard runs out of his office. Give me a week to sweet-talk the Master Rogue, and I'll be able to prove that he's just another Thief out to cheat the school.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f830a6da-91fc-42f9-a61c-dceee366a344",
                                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Good, good! Get me proof of this and Gerhard will be gone for good.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "978d008d-fcc5-4237-879b-a639ea91f179",
                            "text": "Answer Snarkily",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "5243e798-2da5-4585-bcd5-d7ccf9a915b2",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "39",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3f022be7-6f49-4c7b-8bdc-61cef01a0316",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "I learned that Blowhard has a very low opinion about people who encourage other people to do criminal acts... And that he knows something sinister about the local Chief Thief...",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "85a32b7a-1b8c-4d7b-90af-5dd13963944b",
                                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Useless! You had better find out something that can be used to oust Gerhard soon - or you'll be on the street. You do not want to displease me or your Patron.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "7664df3c-03a0-4a98-84de-017142bce05d",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "You do not have much time, Conner. If you find anything of interest about Gerhard, let me know. You must not keep your Patron waiting.",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "7aacf6ee-558d-490c-9443-2b67ce2e4492",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "Now get out of here!",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "02d05560-643a-4891-b207-1c97888687fa",
                    "name": "Fear Pressure",
                    "description": "Terk wasted my time by dragging me into his office just to remind me that my mysterious Patron wants me to find evidence against Gerhard. As if I didn't have more important things on my mind than this!\n\nStill, I gotta wonder... what's going on here? Terk hates the Master. No news there. But my <i>Patron</i> - what's with him? What does a Chief Thief have against Gerhard - and why do I keep getting dragged into it?"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeScene",
                    "sceneId": "f1d169df-e10e-451d-8481-0d0290b7cbbe",
                    "spawnId": "2e1c2cd6-e8d8-4d69-8c37-68f7b246bb96",
                    "fadeTime": 2
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}